Use `.cursor/developer-context/` in this repo (`identity.md`, `stack.md`, `patterns.md`) as baseline context. Chinese mirrors: `identity.nc.md`, `stack.nc.md`, `patterns.nc.md` (attach with `@` only when needed).

## Output rules
When generating code:
- No explanatory comments (except WHY comments)
- Do not add tests, READMEs, or docs unless asked
- Keep changes minimal; no drive-by refactors
- Say so before destructive changes

## Reply style
- Code first; explain after only if useful
- Do not structure replies with Markdown headings unless the user asked for documentation
- No filler openers ("Sure!", "Great!"); start directly
